                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " for case-insensitive comparison can be costly if not supported by an appropriate index. Consider using a collation that supports case-insensitive comparisons natively."
